07054ef3f4154ca3.voiceContent: Newcomers who are learning how to use wind gliders will practice simple exercises in Springvale.

19c458d86be3a5a5.voiceContent: Great! Then what are we waiting for?

222cca3602308a4e.voiceContent: Uh... But what if the smoke changes the color of your ceiling...

24d60aaa884b46c7.voiceContent: Or maybe we can practice together! Let's compete and see who wins!

2965f6bc35b06de1.voiceContent: You built such a spacious campsite — amazing...

2be09ddb85849097.voiceContent: I'm not too fussy about where I stay. After all, as an Outrider, I have to be able to adapt to all kinds of surroundings.

3042e7fd0680b1c9.voiceContent: It doesn't need to be anything sophisticated. I just want to enjoy the feeling of having a meal at home. It's quite different from eating out.

334e49b168deef4b.voiceContent: Uh... I think you might find it a little boring. Besides, in hindsight, let's just say that little Amber was... a bit of a nuisance.

343543ecf2ab46f9.voiceContent: Get ready for the most delicious meal you've ever eaten! ...Even if it takes me a few hundred times.

40c907da4c8197d5.voiceContent: Right, we'll do some steak, and— Oh, wait... you must have had my Outrider's Champion Steak a million times already.

448ca10c08f9cd8c.voiceContent: Most of the buildings in Springvale only have two or three floors, which is an ideal height for those still getting accustomed to gliding.

55c556600c0c2efa.voiceContent: Hmm... I guess I could pick out some excerpts from my adventures if you're interested.

727628780edb7bd7.voiceContent: Huh!? How long have you known about that!?

73a01489b95d79f1.voiceContent: ...But it's still a bit embarrassing to just let someone else read my journal!

82734e040e6e7b08.voiceContent: Restaurants are convenient and all, and you can always trust that the food's gonna be good.

945c9bcb15feef3b.voiceContent: But you only get that special cozy feeling when you're eating at home, you know?

a3ea2c2dbed0b557.voiceContent: ...Ooh, and I know just the dish — today, I'll try my hand at a Sticky Honey Roast!

aa233be3c8e4658e.voiceContent: If I had to, I could even sleep on a tree branch.

b277e9f5360b2978.voiceContent: Hehe, you're so kind to me.

b370bb032a96425d.voiceContent: However, please remember to glide legally! The rules also apply here.

bed4cde28fb26e44.voiceContent: You know what, it's high time I set myself a new culinary challenge.

cf2ae8b4071d343e.voiceContent: Can I practice my archery and scouting techniques here?

d198ec5f9d7a06b6.voiceContent: Don't forget, if you ever need an Outrider, just come find me!

da0657bae49ec282.voiceContent: I mean, if you really wanna know, I'm happy to tell you about it... but only if you promise you won't laugh at me!

dcfd6fed7c9e2836.voiceContent: It's so good to see you!

e2366af43f29d657.voiceContent: Sorry, I'm no good at telling stories. Not like Lisa or my grandfather... They seem to be able to fit a thrilling tale into every conversation.

f1e2ba91fcbd5c70.voiceContent: N—Not that I've been hiding it from anyone, it's just that... well, you'd be flattered to read some of the entries...

f35e743be65b03c3.voiceContent: Good night! Don't stay up too late!

fdb7cfd4926370ec.voiceContent: Anyway, don't worry, this place is great!

10290f312ed979df.voiceContent: #{NICKNAME} is a natural. I knew you'd be fine.

26bf1af09a7b5b02.voiceContent: Well... One shot should be able to blow them up!

30cc8d080274581f.voiceContent: Wow! I can see so far into the temple!

813038f8c93c3f25.voiceContent: The fighting must have got them riled up.

9424895b74f27401.voiceContent: It's so high... Seems like there's something up there.

a849326851e91d3f.voiceContent: Dragon's breath! Is that where the power is coming from?

ba7e2d3aadabd476.voiceContent: All that's left now is to grab ourselves a Raptor — let's go!

c6417f228e0dfe98.voiceContent: You can use that console to open the door.

ce97536dc1c3606e.voiceContent: Okay then. You just need to follow the <color=#00E1FFFF>marked route</color> to the finish.

d6917effd3e11f54.voiceContent: Well, good thing I've prepared my secret weapon <color=#00E1FFFF>Explosive Puppet Baron Bunny</color>!

02e74d666a5e17c6.voiceContent: Uh, I'm just not used to this taste, sorry! Nothing to do with you of course!

0bd03af654d7431c.voiceContent: If only the wind was a little stronger...

0d22b9146f682802.voiceContent: It's getting late, should I light a torch?

10dd33d7c145d36d.voiceContent: It's raining again... This will hinder our vision, we must remain vigilant!

153b9177912f7dc1.voiceContent: I can handle anything and everything! As long as it isn't cold Wolfhook juice... Ugh, yuck...

1be387f4b895c31e.voiceContent: When you have time, we should go see Lisa! Last time I saw her, she was telling me about a story involving a treasure in the Dragonspine area. But, we got cut off before she could finish. I can't wait to hear the rest of her story!

24897a04687ad11c.voiceContent: Baron Bunny, today is another squeaky clean day!

24f0df46a2ea3b6e.voiceContent: The view from the Cathedral's clock tower is amazing! You should check it out.

2deffee5e2a3c5e2.voiceContent: Remember that I don't go easy on anyone, even you!

318217604dfd07f4.voiceContent: At this speed, no one can keep up with me!

3368fca616b34a2e.voiceContent: I wish I was as good at cooking as you...

3520b539700697b5.voiceContent: Another target tracked down by Outrider Amber!

3ae96d02320d1230.voiceContent: Eula is a great friend of mine! You just need to get used to her sense of humor and you'll get along fine! The only reason she's misunderstood by so many people is her family name. How can I get them to see her for who she really is?

3eea9162dd6c9f6f.voiceContent: I love this kind of weather, ahh... so relaxing~

43e432143238e9da.voiceContent: Outrider Amber reporting for duty! Just say the word if you ever need my help!

4db67a3124e5d1bc.voiceContent: Klee? She can be a bit cheeky sometimes, but everyone in the Knights of Favonius likes her. Although... I really ought to keep a closer eye on her if I wanna keep her from getting put in confinement by Jean again.

500f5a67889d73f1.voiceContent: Collei wrote to me saying that her Eleazar has been completely cured... I'm so happy for her! I wish I could fly to her side right now and give her the biggest hug! She also said she misses everyone in Mondstadt, and that once she's ready, she'll come visit us in person and tell us all about her progress... Oh, it would be great if she could make it in time for the next Ludi Harpastum. Aaah I can't wait to see her again!

50b4dfd83564781f.voiceContent: I'll share my ultimate Gliding Champion secret with you! The most important thing to remember, is to have courage!

57d0b4d204417577.voiceContent: You wanna know about Noelle? She's super resilient. Still, since she's younger than us, we should look out for her.

5df4df5514e64fb5.voiceContent: Mondstadt Gliding Champion, yep, that's me! Gliding Champion!

5f2cae8afbd49f5a.voiceContent: Uh, I'm just not used to this taste, sorry! Nothing to do with you of course!

66f8bc391e1ed559.voiceContent: Oh no, now my thoughts are all jumbled up...

6c91893149865738.voiceContent: Morning! Want to go on a jog?

6f968181ce985f2a.voiceContent: Hey, there's something strange over there... C'mon, let's take a look!

761e95fce728fcc1.voiceContent: If Lisa's not sleeping, she'll be reading! I don't know how she does it, I wouldn't be able to sit still for that long.

76909d10c2bd26e8.voiceContent: Get ready for the Gliding Champion of Mondstadt!

7ae558292499fb89.voiceContent: My Vision... Is a sign that the Archons believe in me. Yes, I must become the best Outrider I can possibly be!

7dea90306442a667.voiceContent: Jean makes the most amazing cup of coffee! You'll have to try it sometime.

7fc51ad61fb38ab0.voiceContent: Wow! This is delicious, you're an amazing cook!

80b741dafe5f2619.voiceContent: Hmm? Bennett... I feel like I've heard that name before... Oh! Yes, he's that hot-blooded guy from the Adventurers' Guild, right! I tend to come across him way out in the wild from time to time, he seems to really love treasure hunting.

823d9a3bc3af2ec2.voiceContent: Whoa... You're so much better than everyone I've played against...

85053a3c9bdc1332.voiceContent: Jean might still be working? We should invite her for coffee... Let's go.

88621cee11665c05.voiceContent: When I'm teaching you to glide, I feel like I can go even faster than usual... Huh? What are you laughing at? I'll prove it! We can race — right now!

8aca5156d23dae45.voiceContent: The skies over Mondstadt seem to have gotten smaller... or is it that my sight reaches further than ever before?

8b392f7fffeaf45d.voiceContent: Hey, happy birthday! Here, I have a gift for you an exclusive, custom-made version of Baron Bunny that I sewed for you myself. Uh... don't worry, custom-made means that it won't explode!

8e92ff3b40c7b50c.voiceContent: Albedo spends most of his time in his workshop, tinkering away with all of his awesome stuff. But, when you see him in person, you can never quite tell what he is thinking, not a clue at all.

909872ee8ea4eaeb.voiceContent: There's something weird-looking about the dandelions in the garden... Hmm, I bet Kaeya had something to do with this!

967fd3d2579d9f82.voiceContent: Agreed, getting rest is essential! Let's meet here tomorrow then. See ya!

a1188bc8fc2c5f25.voiceContent: I joined the Knights because of my grandpa, I stayed because of Jean. And now, you're the one that showed me the world beyond Mondstadt. I couldn't be happier.

b203573008b6c452.voiceContent: Opening a chest is like unwrapping a gift!

b32c7b41b3376e24.voiceContent: Wow, these will come in handy!

b6cb1843920fba15.voiceContent: After the Grand Master left on his expedition, all the affairs of the Knights of Favonius, both big and small, have been left up to Jean. If only there was more I could do to help her...

b6e457164620f0f4.voiceContent: Can I get lunch with you?

c0254451da6336f1.voiceContent: Oh... Do you have any idea how to make a decent Moon Pie?

c1061857a451c62f.voiceContent: Oh! Mika's a veteran of Eula's team. When he first arrived, it was always Yes, Commander! every time he spoke to me — I guess it must have been because he saw how close I was with Eula. But then, even after I told him I was actually an Outrider, he still called me Ma'am... It was so embarrassing. We have completely different responsibilities, after all. I definitely could never match his expertise in cartography.

d1b68ca22380d298.voiceContent: Betcha can't keep up with me!

d81eb4718a89844c.voiceContent: Look, there's a pigeon over there! *giggle* I wish I could fly alongside them.

de5ea5479bbc4c6b.voiceContent: Yeah! As fast as riding the wind!

e054eabc7af86d6a.voiceContent: I wish I was as good at cooking as you...

e07f723aea1247b4.voiceContent: Wow! This is delicious, you're an amazing cook!

e154c36f876345d6.voiceContent: It seems that now... I've improved so much compared to when we first met! Hehe, thank you so much! Let me treat you to a Sticky Honey Roast! Let's go, let's go!

e2ea95d0ce5293ea.voiceContent: Oh no, it's raining... now my uniform will get all wet...

e3bbe50740e5a674.voiceContent: ...I'm feeling uneasy all of a sudden! Was that Kaeya with you earlier? Did he give you any trouble?

e54a8d4a9066f110.voiceContent: So you're the one I'll be playing against! It's a real competition this time, so you'd better be ready!

e629d1f2c0fe1e98.voiceContent: I'm a pro at hunting, you know! How about I show you some of my skills? Or even better... how about a little competition?

f483b3798dedd233.voiceContent: Jean will be upset if she catches us lazing around like this.

f679d1d006d13f54.voiceContent: I would like to explore the other worlds beyond. I wanna see how deep the rabbit hole goes! You'll keep me company, right?

f7a2fde1b151f6b6.voiceContent: I'm really not that good with riddles. I always try to avoid the riddles stand during Ludi Harpastum... What about you?

fdd8e841d8de526b.voiceContent: Okay! I need to go over my deck one more time, and if things don't work out... I guess I'll have to ask someone for advice.
